# Orquestrador dnd-api

**Infra:** [`docs/infrastructure.md`](../../docs/infrastructure.md) · **Arquitetura:** [`docs/architecture.md`](../../docs/architecture.md)

Repo **API only**: `database/` + `src/` Nest. Frontend = `dnd-front` (irmão em `dnd-work/`).

Genérico (shared-ai): `nestjs`, `typeorm`, `jest`, `testing`, `sql`, `postgres`, `supabase`, `vercel`, `rest-api`.

## Roteamento local

| Contexto | Rules | Skills locais |
|----------|-------|---------------|
| Arquitetura / BC / CQRS | bounded-contexts, catalog-thin-layer, game-domain, application-layer | nestjs-bounded-context, cqrs-catalog-vs-game |
| REST / erros / testes | rest-api, api-errors, api-testing, api-contract | nestjs-api-tests (+ global `jest`) |
| SQL / migrations / seeds | postgres-sql, supabase-sql, sql-clean-code, sql-oop-patterns, phb-data-model | postgres-apply-catalog, rpg-catalog-model, phb-query-views |
| Nest catálogo | catalog-thin-layer, nestjs-core, nestjs-typeorm, api-contract | nestjs-bounded-context, typeorm-rpg-entities (+ global `typeorm`) |
| Nest game | game-domain, bounded-contexts, supabase-auth | cqrs-catalog-vs-game |
| Deploy Vercel | nestjs-vercel | nest-vercel-deploy (+ global `vercel`) |
| Supabase DB / Auth | supabase-sql, supabase-auth | supabase-auth (+ global `supabase`) |
| Contrato frontend | api-contract | api-consumer-next |
| Glossário PHB PT | — | dnd-glossary-pt |

## Princípios

- **3 BC:** Catalog (thin), Identity (JWT), Game (sheet / build / progression / inventory / session)
- DB + Auth: Supabase · API: Vercel · ORM: TypeORM
- Catálogo read-only público; fichas = JWT + ownership na API
- `database/` source of truth PHB; `synchronize: false`
